	* ThemeWin32Classic.cs: Hook ListViewItems into the ShowFocusCues
	logic.

2008-09-16  Jonathan Pobst  <monkey@jpobst.com>

	* TreeView.cs: Don't start editing a node on right click, only
	left click.

