	* NativeWindow.cs: Reenable the ThreadExceptionDialog I accidentally
	disabled over a year ago.
	* Form.cs: Wrap calling Load in a try/catch because it can happen
	before the catch-all one in NativeWindow.
	[Fixes bug #425414]

