	repopulating subitems.
	* GridEntry.cs: 
	 - Handle null StandardValuesCollection.
	 - Mark as not editable if there is no PropertyDescriptor and
	 if the Converter cannot convert from string.
	[Part of fix for bugs #360666 and #358332]

