	* ListBox.cs : don't perform invalidations if the handle hasn't been
	created.  [Fixes #80753]

2007-03-27  Mike Kestner  <mkestner@novell.com>

	* ListBox.cs : don't adjust top item when SelectedIndex is set to -1.
	[Fixes #80428]

