	* Control.cs: Tweak 2.0 layout properties.
	* Form.cs: Switch ToolStripMenuTracker hooks to ToolStripManager.
	* TextRenderer.cs: Add a new overload.
	* ToolStrip*: Huge amount of changes and new features.

