	* XplatUIX11.cs: the atom we want is _NET_WM_STATE_SKIP_TASKBAR,
	not _NET_WM_STATE_NO_TASKBAR.

2006-11-02  Jackson Harper  <jackson@ximian.com>

	* TextControl.cs: Increment count by one, since in the update view
	count - 1 is used.

