2006-04-05  Jackson Harper  <jackson@ximian.com>

	* Control.cs: Enable OnPaintInternal so we can use it for drawing
	all of our controls instead of Paint +=.
	* ListBox.cs:
	* ListView.cs:
	* MenuAPI.cs:
	* MessageBox.cs:
	* NotifyIcon.cs:
	* ProgressBar.cs:
	* ScrollBar.cs:
	* Splitter.cs:
	* StatusBar.cs:
	* TabControl.cs:
	* TextBoxBase.cs:
	* ToolBar.cs:
	* TrackBar.cs:
	* UpDownBase.cs:
