	* TabControl.cs:
	  - ToString: Added method
	  - CreateParams: Remove TODO and comment
	  - OnKeyDown: Cycle through bounds properly.
	  - SelectedIndex: Scroll to the right or left if we need to
	  display the newly selected tab.

